Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.22,1:00:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想做的事情差不多做了一半的時侯
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.30,1:00:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我再次意識到了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.51,1:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的現狀
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.12,1:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突如其來地 她住院了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.56,1:01:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在她燦爛的笑容下所隱藏的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.83,1:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正逐漸侵蝕著她的身體
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.65,1:01:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我一直都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.80,1:01:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真是白擔心了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.77,1:01:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這麼精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.72,1:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.40,1:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是數值稍微有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.20,1:01:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸媽很擔心 才鬧出這麼大動靜
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.32,1:01:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.09,1:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比起這個
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.26,1:01:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暑假的計劃都泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.69,1:01:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}週末的廟會也去不成了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.02,1:01:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是太倒霉了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.79,1:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正鄰鎮還會再辦的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.55,1:01:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到時再去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.49,1:02:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住院的事情你跟死黨同學是怎麼說的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.08,1:02:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說是盲腸的手術
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.90,1:02:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也讓醫院幫我隱瞞了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.03,1:02:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}班裡的同學說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.45,1:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說你不來上課是因為我在跟蹤你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.31,1:02:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經無言了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.21,1:02:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道為什麼會這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.11,1:02:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為我和你在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.34,1:02:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.48,1:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為你沒有好好跟大家說哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.75,1:02:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你跟大家好好說
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.92,1:02:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家也都會發現 你是個有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.39,1:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有人想和不起眼同學搭話吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.18,1:02:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還和以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.51,1:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在想像大家是怎麼看待自己的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.22,1:02:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不如試試改掉這種習慣？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.01,1:02:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得 你還是應該和班上的大家好好相處
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.86,1:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種對誰都沒好處的事我是不會做的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.64,1:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.68,1:03:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真想讓你和恭子也好好相處呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.16,1:03:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.80,1:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.86,1:03:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.87,1:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次就行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.21,1:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來玩真心話大冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.07,1:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.75,1:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.10,1:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.61,1:03:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也借我書了 只玩一次的話
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.81,1:03:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.69,1:03:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這真是沒想到啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.13,1:03:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.23,1:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這種遊戲嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.91,1:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 問吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.66,1:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什麼都會回答的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.42,1:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要問初吻的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.57,1:03:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 不要無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.96,1:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再對我感興趣一點啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.80,1:03:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要先學會對別人感興趣才行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.51,1:03:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對你來說
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.43,1:04:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活著是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.89,1:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼認真啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.35,1:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.88,1:04:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想想
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.64,1:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.28,1:04:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活著就是
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.08,1:04:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和某人心意相通
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.96,1:04:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.48,1:04:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才叫活著吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.23,1:04:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}認可某人 喜歡上某人 討厭某人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.00,1:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和某人在一起會感到開心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.92,1:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和某人牽手 這就是活著
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.85,1:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自己一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.57,1:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就感覺不到自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.04,1:05:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有和別人產生關聯 才算是活著
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.67,1:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.26,1:05:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的心靈 是為了和大家交流
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.21,1:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的身體 是為了和大家接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.48,1:05:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.27,1:05:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人活著是有意義的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.58,1:05:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是由自己來選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.49,1:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像你和我現在在這裡活著一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.91,1:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.16,1:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.19,1:05:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的教會了我許多
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.63,1:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了突然
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.44,1:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.15,1:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.49,1:06:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.42,1:06:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.27,1:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和之前不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.78,1:06:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.08,1:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.44,1:06:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近不知怎麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.34,1:06:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特別喜歡人的體溫
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.56,1:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是不是有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.04,1:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 我什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.87,1:06:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.80,1:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想品味你給我的真實和日常
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.55,1:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.05,1:06:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭子
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.63,1:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.60,1:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上次的事情還沒…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.95,1:07:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭子
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.01,1:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.06,1:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.76,1:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然因為盲腸而住院什麼的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.13,1:07:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你別走
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.27,1:07:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭子一來我就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.31,1:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}櫻良 現在我要找那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.41,1:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}櫻良 放開我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.59,1:07:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.45,1:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要恭子的體溫
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.75,1:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之後要多少給你多少啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.56,1:07:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}櫻良
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.68,1:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天恭子來了？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.40,1:07:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把換洗衣物放這裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.99,1:07:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.84,1:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.21,1:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我死了之後
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.18,1:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}櫻良
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.15,1:08:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要說死不死的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.69,1:08:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有件事想拜託您
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.06,1:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然還早
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.29,1:08:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在病房裡從她身上感受到的違和感
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.21,1:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種感覺的理由
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.82,1:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.34,1:08:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\an1\frz5.422\c&H957E5A&\3c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H1E&\frx2\fry0\move(627,873.499,573,815.499,0,6993)}出院又要延後兩週了\N傍晚要來探望我哦！！
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.10,1:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的住院時間 比預定延長了兩週
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.11,1:08:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放學後 我馬上去了醫院
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.67,1:08:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坦白的說
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.36,1:08:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我非常地擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.62,1:09:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這是準備幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.19,1:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從醫院溜出來沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.29,1:09:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.72,1:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊來
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.04,1:09:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是想找個沒人的地方拉我殉情嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.62,1:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好主意
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.00,1:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這裡還能看到醫院
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.36,1:09:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一般人絕對不知道這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.95,1:09:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜景的話出院後再看也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.73,1:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必須是今天才行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.26,1:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然你最近很反常啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.25,1:10:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不會死吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.60,1:10:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然會死啊 我和你都會
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.91,1:10:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.45,1:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是說胰臟的事 那當然也會死
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.57,1:10:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.59,1:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別看這樣其實我也是很擔心你的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.58,1:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想讓我… 活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.43,1:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 非常想
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.38,1:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.63,1:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然有人這麼關心我 我好幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.54,1:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 死的時候我一定會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.39,1:11:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始了哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
