Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.84,1:11:33.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}瞼開いて
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.84,1:11:33.53,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}張開雙眼
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.57,1:11:37.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}残る夜の残像
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.57,1:11:37.94,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}腦中還殘留著夜晚的餘景
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.64,1:11:42.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}枕に沈む
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.64,1:11:42.26,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}把頭埋進枕頭
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.62,1:11:45.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記憶の欠片
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.62,1:11:45.12,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記憶拼湊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.26,1:11:49.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夏の夜の夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.26,1:11:49.97,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}又夢到了那個夏夜的夢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.91,1:11:54.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}朧げな五感
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.91,1:11:54.02,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}感官逐漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.05,1:11:56.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}抜け落ちたまま
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.05,1:11:56.76,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}彷彿就要掉下去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.76,1:11:59.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}その手を掴んで
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.76,1:11:59.79,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}卻被你緊緊抓住
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.93,1:12:06.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}体温が移るまで
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.93,1:12:06.28,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}直到能傳遞到彼此的溫度為止
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.78,1:12:11.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}内緒だよ
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.78,1:12:11.46,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.63,1:12:14.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢で見たこと
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.63,1:12:14.61,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}我們夢中所見之事
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.61,1:12:16.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}思い出しでさ
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.61,1:12:16.76,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}回想起來的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.81,1:12:20.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}嬉しくなるなんで
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.81,1:12:20.75,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}也會會心一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.75,1:12:23.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}内緒だよ
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.75,1:12:23.06,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.18,1:12:26.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢で見たこと
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.18,1:12:26.14,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}我們夢中所發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.33,1:12:28.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}叶うなんでさ
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.33,1:12:28.46,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}可以實現的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.46,1:12:35.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}温かい腕のなか
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.46,1:12:35.41,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}在你溫暖的臂彎裡
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.80,1:12:42.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}覚めない
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.80,1:12:42.31,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此美妙的夢裡
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.31,1:12:44.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢の中で
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.31,1:12:44.36,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}不願醒來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.98,1:13:27.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}両目を擦て
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.98,1:13:27.47,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}輕揉雙目
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.90,1:13:30.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}瞼開いて
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.90,1:13:30.59,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}張開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.59,1:13:35.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}今日も同じ夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.59,1:13:35.48,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}今天也做了個同樣的夢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.42,1:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(990,1060.5)}之前不是說了嗎 想去看煙火
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.32,1:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以必須得是今天才行
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.25,1:11:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能來真是太好了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.18,1:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒是不否定
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.14,1:11:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.32,1:11:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.50,1:11:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我個回禮
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.81,1:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓你白擔心了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.20,1:12:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(1020.715,1057.5)}作為補償 出院後我會陪你去海邊的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.34,1:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還真是傲慢的補償呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.53,1:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.97,1:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並不討厭
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.77,1:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出院後的約定
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.17,1:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總感覺她的行為是不是預示著什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.91,1:13:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(1125.215,1057.5)}雖然有過不安 不過只是杞人憂天罷了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.57,1:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她出院的日子 不久就到了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.89,1:13:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an1\c&H575257&\3c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H1E&\frx2\fry0\pos(729.857,690.643)\frz19.3}上午就出院啦！\N一起吃午餐吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.02,1:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.82,1:13:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.92,1:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是交女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.58,1:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.62,1:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是喜歡的女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.80,1:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是什麼下次把她帶到家裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.40,1:14:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪邊都不是 不會帶來的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.11,1:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那只是普通朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.58,1:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正怎麼都行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.09,1:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一次有人能好好的看待你 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.94,1:14:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以為我不知道你在說謊嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.97,1:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別小看你老媽
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.41,1:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天也好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.72,1:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是要去哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.84,1:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微跟人碰個頭
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.57,1:14:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊又是櫻良嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.06,1:14:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真羨慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.53,1:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回見
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.39,1:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要口香糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.16,1:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 我不吃
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.70,1:15:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛就只有哥哥你一個人吃了冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.19,1:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.86,1:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}狡猾狡猾！
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.18,1:15:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停手停手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.80,1:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\fs60}射你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.02,1:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不買這東西買冰淇淋不就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.15,1:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說了停手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.08,1:15:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了啦 給你們買
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.36,1:15:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好嘞 咱倆去挑吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.87,1:15:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}口香糖…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.44,1:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}口香糖 還是給我一塊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.64,1:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.05,1:15:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接著
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.97,1:15:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好球！
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.17,1:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玩的開心點
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.72,1:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.41,1:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺自己變了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.36,1:15:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前對人從不感興趣的我
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.27,1:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知不覺被她改變了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.73,1:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 如果按她的話來說
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.20,1:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是自己選擇了改變吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.62,1:16:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}選擇把丟在地上的共病文庫撿起來
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.24,1:16:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}選擇了接受她的邀請
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.34,1:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也選擇了與她在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.73,1:16:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.11,1:16:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛出門
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.14,1:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭喜出院
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.94,1:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在在Cafe Spring等你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.02,1:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還記得那家店啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.91,1:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我正好在考慮你的事
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.17,1:16:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真稀奇 你居然會說出這麼讓人開心的話
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.83,1:16:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 生病了？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.01,1:16:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟你不一樣我可是很健康的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.64,1:16:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好過分！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.96,1:16:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你傷害到我了！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.89,1:16:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作為懲罰我要你現在誇我！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.78,1:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是個厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.42,1:17:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是和我完全相反的人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.67,1:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我肯定 一直想成為你這樣的人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.69,1:17:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能接受別人 能被人接受
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.33,1:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能愛別人 能被愛
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.77,1:17:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.55,1:17:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼樣才能像你這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.37,1:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\pos(976.5,708)\frz6.136\c&H7E655A&\3c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H32&\3a&H32&\frx5}我想以你為榜樣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.01,1:17:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H7E655A&\3c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H32&\3a&H32&\pos(779.357,600)\frz355.1\frx2}我想吃掉你的胰臟
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.60,1:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝您的惠顧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.06,1:18:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs45\pos(1069.715,409.5)\frz345.9\c&H838982&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frx8}正在獲取新郵件
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.81,1:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs45\c&H838982&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1074.858,392.357)\frz345.9\frx8}沒有新郵件
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.43,1:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\fs60}下一則新聞
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.24,1:18:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8\fs60}今日傍晚
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.50,1:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3\fs60}在北方町市街邊發現了一位被刀具刺傷的十七歲女高中生
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.42,1:18:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不就在附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.32,1:18:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.83,1:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.00,1:18:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}據知情人事的消息  被害者是在市內上學的高中生
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.62,1:18:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山內櫻良 17歲
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.04,1:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發現時已經被刀具刺中胸部倒在了路邊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.45,1:19:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs60\an8}發現後不久 通過目擊者的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.69,1:19:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs60\an8}救護車很快就把重傷昏迷的山內送到了醫院
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.07,1:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不久後便確認死亡
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.14,1:19:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犯罪嫌疑人現已被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.89,1:19:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.19,1:19:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.49,1:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.47,1:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她沒能履行死之前會通知我的諾言
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.13,1:20:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也沒能履行把她借我的東西還給她的諾言
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.23,1:20:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她 死了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.65,1:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她去世之後 我迎來了第十個早晨
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.70,1:20:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我總算能夠冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.94,1:20:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接受了她死去的事實
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.99,1:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}整理了心情之後 我想清楚了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.01,1:21:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我下定決心
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.04,1:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要去面對 故事最後的結局
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.14,1:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你 去和她好好道別吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.07,1:21:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}櫻良在世時 真的受到她很多照顧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.40,1:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 我有話想和您說
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.52,1:21:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.07,1:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 知道她生病的事
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.20,1:21:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是從她口中得知的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.52,1:22:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 我真的沒想到她會出這種事
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.10,1:22:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她對除我之外的人都隱瞞了病情
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.02,1:22:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我來這裡還有一個目的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.24,1:22:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想看一下 她生病之後寫的日記
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.61,1:22:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「共病文庫」
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.98,1:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來…是你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.10,1:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.71,1:22:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.67,1:22:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能來
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.80,1:22:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.11,1:22:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.01,1:22:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.02,1:22:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能讓我 看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.93,1:22:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.58,1:22:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.69,1:22:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是櫻良留給你的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.45,1:23:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從櫻良那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.84,1:23:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她說等她死後
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.25,1:23:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想把這本日記交給一個人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.48,1:23:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唯一一個 知道自己病情
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.40,1:23:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道「共病文庫」的人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.01,1:23:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人很膽小 可能不會出席葬禮
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.47,1:23:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過他一定會來取這本日記的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.22,1:23:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你 真的非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.51,1:23:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多虧了你 那孩子才能…
