Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.47,1:46:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟我是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.33,1:46:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就讓我先發幾句牢騷吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.44,1:46:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並沒有你想的那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.94,1:46:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要與人產生聯繫 真的好困難
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.37,1:46:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以這花了我一年時間
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.31,1:46:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我終於走到了這一步
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.84,1:46:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我一年前所選擇的路
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.03,1:46:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了成為像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.97,1:46:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成為能夠認可別人 能夠愛別人的人
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.78,1:46:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.88,1:46:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會試著一個人走下去的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.96,1:47:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 再會了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.12,1:47:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}變得幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.24,1:47:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說啥
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.88,1:47:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到櫻良墓前向我表白嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.11,1:47:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真可怕
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.16,1:47:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.90,1:47:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是更深層的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.01,1:47:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.12,1:47:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.34,1:47:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你原來喜歡口香糖啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.74,1:47:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近開始的啦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.67,1:47:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.19,1:47:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交往也要等考完試以後了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.49,1:47:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這次考試他絕對會很用功吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.90,1:48:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.90,1:48:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要去櫻良家了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.62,1:48:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 櫻良在等我們了
